  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe `AttestationAggregator` implementation is rather naive.\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\n- Stores all `Attestations` in-memory.\r\n- Never deletes `Attestations`.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nIt should have a sane memory management strategy.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\n1. Figure out a sensible strategy.\r\n2. Discuss it here.\r\n3. Implement it, once it is agreed upon.\r\n",
